    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>python 练手题目</p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="a-b"><a href="#a-b" class="headerlink" title="a+b"></a>a+b</h3><p>输入两个整数 a 和 b，计算 a+b 的和</p><p>注意此题是多组测试数据</p><p>解一：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">while True:</span><br><span class="line">#while True 语句中一定要有结束该循环的 break 语句，否则会一直循环下去的 </span><br><span class="line">    try:</span><br><span class="line">    #Python 中，用 try except 语句块捕获并处理异常 </span><br><span class="line">        a,b&#x3D;map (int,input ().strip ().split ())</span><br><span class="line">        if a&gt;2**10 or b&gt;2**10:</span><br><span class="line">            break</span><br><span class="line">        print (a+b)</span><br><span class="line">    except:</span><br><span class="line">        break</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>解二：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">while True:</span><br><span class="line">    a&#x3D;list (map (int,input ().split ())) </span><br><span class="line">    #定义列表 a</span><br><span class="line">    b&#x3D;len (a) </span><br><span class="line">    #len () 方法返回对象（字符、列表、元组等）长度或项目个数 </span><br><span class="line">    c&#x3D;0 </span><br><span class="line">    #计算总和，sum 作用 </span><br><span class="line">    for i in range (0,b):</span><br><span class="line">    #for 循环，range () 是一个函数， for i in range () 就是给 i 赋值，range (start, stop [, step])，分别是起始、终止和步长 </span><br><span class="line">        if (a [i]&lt;2**10): </span><br><span class="line">    #判断是否题目定义满足条件 </span><br><span class="line">            c+&#x3D;a [i] </span><br><span class="line">    #计算总和 </span><br><span class="line">    print (&quot;&#123;&#125;&quot;.format (c)) </span><br><span class="line">    #格式化字符串的函数 str.format ()，它增强了字符串格式化功能，format 函数可以接受不限个参数，位置可以不按顺序 </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
